
run_game v 0.2
console test version
========

simple game where you need to escape from enemies. written in c++

to make you need sfml-1.6 library, which you can download on http://sfml-dev.org/

after that, just cd to the sources folder and copy to terminal:

g++ model.cpp ai.cpp application.cpp player.cpp gameexception.cpp gamer.cpp main.cpp menu.cpp options.cpp view.cpp -o main -lsfml-graphics -lsfml-window -lsfml-system

then ./main to run the game

(c) 2012, Filippov Roman

